title: Anand - Carlsen World Chess Match 2013 (gnv64)
description:
The chess world championship match was recently held at Chennai, India between defending champion GM Vishwanathan Anand of India & the Norwegian boy prodigy GM Magnus Carlsen. It was convincingly won by Carlsen and the future of chess is in great hands!
I have scanned two cover articles on the same from a weekly Indian sports magazine 'Sportstar'. 'Face-Off' was published just before the match began & 'Sky is the Limit' was published after Carlsen had won the title. I hope chess-lovers will like these....
